randoop.types

Class ConcreteTypeBound

  • java.lang.Object
    • randoop.types.TypeBound
      • randoop.types.ConcreteTypeBound

  • public class ConcreteTypeBound
extends TypeBound
    Represents a concrete type that occurs as a bound on a type parameter in a class, interface, method or constructor (see JLS 7 section 4.4).

        public java.lang.Class<?> getRuntimeClass()
        Description copied from class: TypeBound
